Pathfinder
Circles pathfinder calculates “how much and through which tokens can flow from A to B” based on trust and balances (wrapped and unwrapped). You can use it to:
Preview a route and achievable amount.
Feed
```
TransferBuilder
```
or custom
```
operateFlowMatrix
```
calls.
